    <h1 class="text-center mt-5">RESTURN PRODUCT</h1>

    <!-- FAQ AREA START (faq-2) (ID > accordion_2) -->
    <div class="ltn__faq-area mb-100 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="ltn__faq-inner ltn__faq-inner-2">
                        <!--  -->
                        <div id="accordion_2">
                            <!-- card -->
                            <div class="card">
                                <h6 class="collapsed ltn__card-title" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-item-2-1" aria-expanded="false">
                                    Product damage, but shiping box OK.
                                </h6>
                                <div id="faq-item-2-1" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion_2">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>If your product arrives damaged, but the shipping box is undamaged, you can initiate a return. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and will promptly replace the damaged item or issue a refund. Please ensure to take photos of the damaged product and retain the original packaging for the return process. </p>
                                         <button class="btn-dark" onclick="addToWishlist('<%= orderId %>')" >Return.</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- card -->
                            <div class="card">
                                <h6 class="ltn__card-title" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-item-2-2" aria-expanded="false"> 
                                    Both products and shiping box damage.
                                </h6>
                                <div id="faq-item-2-2" class="collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordion_2">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>If both the product and shipping box arrive damaged, we understand your frustration. In this case, please initiate a return, and we will swiftly arrange for a replacement or issue a refund. To facilitate the return process, kindly provide images of both the damaged product and the damaged shipping box. </p>
                                         <button class="btn-dark" onclick="addToWishlist('<%= orderId %>')" >Return.</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>                          
                            <!-- card -->
                            <div class="card">
                                <h6 class="collapsed ltn__card-title" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-item-2-3" aria-expanded="false">
                                    Wrong item was sent.
                                </h6>
                                <div id="faq-item-2-3" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion_2">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>If you received an incorrect item, we sincerely apologize for the mix-up. Rest assured, we'll make it right. Initiate a return and let us know about the error. We'll arrange for the correct item to be sent to you as quickly as possible. In the meantime, you can keep the incorrect item, and we'll cover the return shipping costs. </p>
                                         <button class="btn-dark" onclick="addToWishlist('<%= orderId %>')" >Return.</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- card -->
                            <div class="card">
                                <h6 class="collapsed ltn__card-title" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-item-2-4" aria-expanded="false">
                                    I don't like the color or Products.
                                </h6>
                                <div id="faq-item-2-4" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion_2">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <p>We understand that personal preferences can vary, and sometimes the product received may not match your expectations. In such cases, you can initiate a return within our specified return period. Simply send the item back to us in its original condition, and upon receipt, we will process a refund or offer an exchange for an alternative product. </p>
                                        <button class="btn-dark" onclick="addToWishlist('<%= orderId %>')">Return.</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- card -->                         
                        </div>
                        <!--  -->
                        <div class="need-support text-center mt-100">
                            <h2>Still need help? Reach out to support 24/7:</h2>
                            <div class="btn-wrapper mb-30">
                                <a href="#" class="theme-btn-1 btn">Contact Us</a>
                            </div>
                            <h3><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +0123-456-789</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- FAQ AREA START -->

    <!-- CALL TO ACTION START (call-to-action-6) -->
